// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2024-0294 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 1eea42eb-61b7-5eea-b7d0-6c49242e7605

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:8*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:16.04-ESM*")
